quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  59,17,"Ne niiba indukho yabu babili mbu toto bo balimumulilo tsinyanga tsioosi, ne oko niko omurungo kwa Abamabii."
  59,18,"Enywe abasuubila, rie Nyasaye, ne buli shia mundu ahenge nishina shiayekasilia khulwa mutsuli. Ne rie Nyasaye. Toto Nyasaye nomumanyi po khukamukholanga."
  59,19,"Ne mulaba shinga balia bebilila Nyasaye mana nabakhola nibeyibilila abeene tawe. Abo nibo abarulanga mumalako."
  59,20,"Shibayelana tawe Abandu bomulilo nende Abandu bomwikulu. Abandu bomwikulu nibo abalibura."
  59,21,"Khuleshinjiakho Ikurani ino khushikulu, wakhashilutsi nishiriire muno nishiatikhana khulwokhuria Nyasaye. Ne endio nilwa khuchelasilinjia Abandu bakhaba bario banyoola okhupara."
  59,22,"Ye niye Nyasaye, abulao nyasaye wundi ulali Ye tawe. Omumanyi wakefisa nende kalolekha, naye ni Omunji wetsimbabaasi, Omukoosia muno."
  59,23,"Ye niye Nyasaye, abulao nyasaye wundi ulali Ye tawe. Omwaami, Woluyali, Womulembe, Omureri Womulembe, Uchesinjia amakhuwake omwene, Owaamani, Ukholanga liayenya, Omukhongo, obutswenufu ni bwa Nyasaye, ali ehale nende akabamusanjinjia."
  59,24,"Ye niye Nyasaye Omuloonji, Omukaasi, Uretsangakhwo obukoondo, ali nende ameera amalayi muno. Bimutswenulanga bioosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo, naye niye Woluyali, Owamachesi muno."